            "review": {
              "id": "12675",
              "reviewer": "Choice",
              "description": "\"A passionate attack on pervasive American cultural assumptions of natural inequality. The book provides a fine history of antiblack discrimination and of the racist and nativist bases of the developers of standardized intelligence tests.\"",
